{"tid":1119640,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"指導未成年男學生變發生關係　女教練被控誘拐兒童罪","createTime":"2019-04-22T05:27:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-22T05:56:46.000Z","uid":126866,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"30aafcf3084b1bb24082131f9536895e9779873b","tid":1119640,"uid":126866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T05:27:11.000Z","msg":"美國印第安納州韋恩堡一名高中女體育教練，前年與一名未成年的男學生交換聯絡方法，希望藉此指導對方，詎料雙方其後發生關係。女體育教練更一度哀求男學生的母親，希望這段不倫的師生關係能夠持續下去。她最終被控兩項誘拐兒童罪，將於周二（23日）出庭應訊。 <br />\n<br />\n案情指，26歲的普西（Cayla Pusey）曾為一間高中擔任體育教練，前年4月與一名男學生交換聯絡方法。雙方其後互傳裸照和情慾短訊，最終發展成性關係。男學生供稱，自己曾經到過普西的家約5至10次。 <br />\n<br />\n普西曾經聯絡男學生的母親，希望對方容許兩人繼續交往，不過遭到拒絕。男學生的母親其後要求兩人結束關係，並承諾只要普西願意離開就不會報警。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20190422/mobile/bkn-20190422030054299-0422_00972_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20190422%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190422030054299-0422_00972_001.html&d=1KnBewcMxCifpJVTRQbR6h1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=a257db24\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20190422/mobile/bkn-20190422030054299-0422_00972_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"2e378b72ed6c2fd341bd7fc594a7349292572bcd","tid":1119640,"uid":109655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T05:28:32.000Z","msg":"點解冇人指導我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24c4224d20362c856f4f8d3dd2d702fa64238424","tid":1119640,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T05:28:59.000Z","msg":"不用貼圖，謝謝！"},{"pid":"3844721e595b564c4e75760d08047ff8d52e05c3","tid":1119640,"uid":156424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e378b72ed6c2fd341bd7fc594a7349292572bcd","tid":1119640,"uid":109655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T05:28:32.000Z","msg":"點解冇人指導我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T05:30:11.000Z","msg":"快點強姦你<img src=\"/assets/face